Revision history for Perl extension SDL_perl.

* 2.516
  - Fix for test plan in t/sdlx_sound [FROGGS]

* 2.515
	- Added preliminary SDLx::Sound [rflipo] 
	- Added preliminary SDLx::TTF [kthakore]

* 2.514
	- Made SDLx::Controller::Interface [kthakore]
